line_1: As People marry now, and settle;
line_2: Fierce Love abates his usual Mettle:

line_1: This fine lone hand some of my debts will settle;
line_2: 'Tis but my due to ride on my own cattle.

line_1: " Sir TOBY MAC'NEGUS is going to settle
line_2: "His Tea-drinking Night with Sir PHILIP O'KETTLE."
